---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About | Kesem Records">
  <section class="about">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>
        Kesem Records is a sound design and music production studio
        founded by Avichai Tuchman (DoGBeaT). We specialize in crafting
        sonic experiences that bridge the gap between technology and
        emotion &mdash; from retro funk to classical remixes, from
        electronic beats to cinematic scores.
      </p>

      <h2>DoGBeaT</h2>
      <p>
        I'm Avichay Tuchman, AKA DoGBeaT &mdash; a musician who embodies the
        energy of '80s French disco with the raw power of rock 'n' roll.
        When I'm not rocking out with the folk-punk band
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@OyDivision" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Oy Division</a>,
        you'll find me in the studio, crafting infectious melodies for
        TV series, theater productions, and my own solo projects.
      </p>
      <p>
        A multi-instrumentalist and mix technician, I've spent the last
        decade producing and playing for a diverse range of artists &mdash;
        from
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6G7rzlSWPQ4" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Shlomi Shaban</a>,
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XVO2ubqcDVU" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Shuli Rand</a>,
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dBdmci7WtUw" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Sofi Tsedaka</a> and
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TZQksnr9ofs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Shai Lahav</a>
        to my duo with
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rqFYO72tGAM" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Noa Faran</a>
        (Universal Music Group) &mdash; many of whom have become radio
        regulars. My passion for music transcends genre, drawing inspiration
        from everything that grooves and moves the soul.
      </p>
      <p>
        I also compose for screen &mdash; scoring TV series for
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLt40gjLOZkQ7V6msfroZyzXo1CdHA4AmC" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Kan 11</a>
        with Assaf Talmudi, and creating music for film and theater.
      </p>
      <p>
        With a knack for blending catchy hooks with unexpected twists,
        my music is sure to get you moving and leave you wanting more.
      </p>

      <h2>What We Do</h2>
      <p>
        Music production, composition, arrangement, sound design, mixing
        and mastering. All tracks composed, performed, and mixed in-house.
        Our music is available for licensing through Artlist for creators
        worldwide.
      </p>

      <h2>Approach</h2>
      <p>
        We believe in precision without sterility. Each sound is
        intentional, each silence meaningful. Our process combines analog
        warmth with digital precision, vintage character with modern
        clarity.
      </p>

      <h2>Genres</h2>
      <div class="genres">
        <span class="genre">Retro</span>
        <span class="genre">Electronic</span>
        <span class="genre">Funk</span>
        <span class="genre">Rock</span>
        <span class="genre">Hip Hop</span>
        <span class="genre">Pop</span>
        <span class="genre">Reggae</span>
        <span class="genre">Lounge</span>
        <span class="genre">Soul & RnB</span>
        <span class="genre">Indie</span>
        <span class="genre">Corporate</span>
        <span class="genre">Classical Remix</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .about h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .divider {
    width: 60px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .content {
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .content p a {
    color: var(--fg);
  }

  .content h2 {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .genres {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }

  .genre {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--accent);
  }
</style>
